      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Dear Hackclubers, \nThank you for playing my game and reading the devlogs
    (I assume you did because I put the secret code in one but if you found this
    on your own amazing work). I learned unity in 2023 but only really started programming
    in 2024. I also got into electronics in March 2025. Well if you read this whole
    thing go comment \"Hacker That Found It\" on the 2nd devlog of this project.
    \n\n-Luke-\n:]"
